    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan for a Class II CPB device. Validation against the FDA generic centrifugal pump benchmark demonstrates adequate model fidelity (NIH MAPE 8.3 %, within 15 % threshold). The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met at all 5 operating points. The credibility evidence package supports the regulatory decision that the CFD model is fit for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
